reviews.review_text: Liked it when I was there Was a god show, as it was for a 86 event. In California, OH.

Real good sound This show sounds real good considering they only played this place twice both years the tapers got the sound rite.   Thank you for the sound here. Not best set list but the sound is a make up. 4 stars because of all the factors
